subject: Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: The freshman Breanna Stewart had 20 points and 10 rebounds to help No. 2 Connecticut continue to roll through the Paradise Jam tournament in St. Thomas, with an 81-39 win over Marist.
